{"tid":1153929,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"教大師訓畢業生 起薪2.7萬創新高","createTime":"2019-05-14T03:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T10:57:01.000Z","uid":138707,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"32612a663569fd7234670d25944c7c22017ed39c","tid":1153929,"uid":138707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T03:01:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/2001974-%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2-%E3%80%90%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%E3%80%91%E6%95%99%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%AB%E8%A8%93%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9F+%E8%B5%B7%E8%96%AA2.7%E8%90%AC%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F2001974-%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2-%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25A8%2593%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2594%259F%2B%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%2596%25AA2.7%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT19PyQTEnBXXUT3Ba6PvfAw%3D&h=b3accc7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F2001974-%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2-%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25A8%2593%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2594%259F%2B%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%2596%25AA2.7%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598&h=fa051194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/2001974-%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2-%E3%80%90%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%E3%80%91%E6%95%99%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%AB%E8%A8%93%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9F+%E8%B5%B7%E8%96%AA2.7%E8%90%AC%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98</a><br />\n<br />\n隨着官津中小學教師職位新學年陸續全面學位化，教師的薪酬待遇亦會提高。教育大學調查去年的畢業生薪酬水平，師訓課程畢業生平均起薪點近<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">27k</span>，是歷年新高，較上一屆上升百分之七點一。教大預料中小學教師職位全面學位化後，起薪點將升至約<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">33k</span>，並料平均薪金將持續上升。<br />\n<br />\n教大學生事務處每年均會進行畢業生就業情況調查，去年成功訪問674名全日制教育榮譽學士課程及學位教師教育文憑課程（PGDE）的應屆畢業生。在560名就讀學士課程的受訪畢業生中。調查顯示就讀師訓課程的畢業生，平均起薪近27k；而就讀非師訓課程，如社會科學、心理學等學科的學生，平均薪酬則為14.4k。<br />\n<br />\n教大署理學生事務處處長甄玉媚表示，過去兩年，政府已額外投放八十三億元「教育新資源」恒常性開支，而下學年官津中小學教師職位將全面學位化，料起薪點將大幅提升至33.3k，教師平均薪金將持續上升。<br />\n<br />\n被問到下學年適齡小一生人數再跌，會否影響畢業生就業，甄玉媚稱，教師人手會自然流失，「現時小學教師約有27000人，流失率為約14%，即每年有1000個空缺，足以吸納教育學位的畢業生。」她又指，教育局將因應學生人數而縮減每班收生人數，相信可減低超額教師的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>狗衝EDU<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3a6853863e663d1de769f1875aee1cfaee01b18b","tid":1153929,"uid":1751,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T03:03:29.000Z","msg":"讀唔成書既垃圾既福音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d31a6a14bc9538cc176e66467d3e1aa950d150","tid":1153929,"uid":40867,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T04:49:13.000Z","msg":"唉 執柒左佢啦<br />\n咪害鳩人得唔得"},{"pid":"bd42dd35c29b915e3993d3776a6fa7bc0c544d22","tid":1153929,"uid":167464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:17:42.000Z","msg":"好後悔當年無去讀edu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c6c7e9802231b59eb1817d8d4bb465d01615aa","tid":1153929,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:20:56.000Z","msg":"好事，香港多d高質老師"},{"pid":"bae87df6f5936a8ff74d4f8a085448f96e09b007","tid":1153929,"uid":53278,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:41:59.000Z","msg":"D老師一係公開試低分入教院<br />\n一係就出面撈唔掂讀pgde入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2679bd0f4c5656772eeb696518666f452cf232b"